</table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/ucefias.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cefias</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><b>RA Member</span><br>  Posts: 73<br> <font color=#006400>(8/9/01 8:54:22 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Advice for young bards, The Meta-Advice</span><hr size=1> Just a little hint, if you really have the timing of twisting down, and your connection is very clean, you can get four songs up 100% of the time. There's a split second between when the effect will kick in and the message to that effect appears. If you time your twisting so your song ends right before the effect shows, you can get four songs up all the time. You'll see something like this:<br>
<br>
You begin playing random_bard_tune_01.<br>
(wait wait wait NOW!)<br>
Your song ends.<br>
The aura of random_bard_tune_01 seeps from your pores and does something really u8er.<br>
<br>
